title: Apartment for Rent
posting_body: First Floor Spacious 1BD/1BA Unit for rent, available August 1st, can be visited starting next week, early move-in possible.
8132 - 8134 S Maryland Ave, Chicago IL 60619 - 6 Unit Building.
Heating/Water/Sewer/Garbage/Cooking Gas included in monthly rent.
Detached 2 car garage in the back of the building, 2 spots available for $50/mo/car.
Tenant pays his own electric bill.
$55 non-refundable online Application and Screening Fee through Turbotenant.
Please do not apply if past evictions on record, you will not be considered.
